ygData.subject: RE: [eqbards] Zone Guides
ygData.msgSnippet: I like Allakhazam s site as it points to the best maps/guides that each area has. http://everquest.allakhazam.com/ But eqmaps is nice as you can read players
ygData.messageBody:
I like Allakhazam's site as it points to the best maps/guides that each area
has.

http://everquest.allakhazam.com/

But eqmaps is nice as you can read players' comments on the various area.
The drawback to this is you do get some bogus info.
